window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The War ended. Lustburg won and Setsuna, Sol's ever loyal Wolf knight, officially became the Queen of Wratharis, the Beastmen Kingdom.</b></p> <p>After a long war, it's now time for Sol and his lovers to have a much deserved rest. The conquest of the Mortal Realm can wait.</p> <p>Still, amidst the preparation for his crowning and wedding, some Kingdoms are on the move.</p> <p>The Angels of Slothein and the Dwarves of Greed Dike seem to be working together. While the Demons of Envilya stay divided.</p> <p>Visiting, Southern Pride, the Elf Kingdom and establishing an official alliance is imperative.</p> <p><b>Becoming close to Satella, the Elf Queen and Jasmine, their Saintess, is just a nice bonus.</b></p>"; 
